User Extracted Data

SelectedbdData.Rd

SelectedbdData is subset of biodiversity data corresponding to search by user search for species by their vernacularName and scientificName.

Usage

SelectedbdData(
  radioBtn_search_byName,
  radioBtn_search_byNameID,
  searchByVerOrSciName,
  selectedByVerOrSciName
)

Arguments

searchedVerncularNameID

and searchedScientifNameID are input ids of Search Species by Vernacular Name and Search Species by scientific Name
